        DeAndre Dean at Belle Isle Conservancy.
        1 July at 00:15 · Instagram ·

        After the pain there will be pleasure.
        I know this road can be misleading but you won't be lost forever.
        Don't hold on to tight to the thoughts of "togethers"
        Because the only thing promised is you and your solo endeavors.
        We are all just trying to grow, praying that our grass is greener. ...
        Forgetting that to ourselves we should only strain to be the pleaser.
        Trying to find peace in this chaos of a mind,
        Trying to take a break and slow down as we speed through time.
        Trapped in my mind.
        A loose grip on reality, but I'm doing just fine.
        If you're ever looking for me I'll be right here.
        Growing in every direction that the path isn't clear.
